# that our API requires, such as:
#   - SECRETS/SESSION KEYS
#   - CREDENTIALS
#   - API KEYS
#   - CONFIGURATION INFO
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. copy file `.env.example` into `.env`
#   2. modify/add any ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES in the `.env` file
